{"tid":1190594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"處決英皇　合理還是不合理？","createTime":"2019-06-07T11:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T11:43:47.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0b34fb41d909604695ce37715ec363cec22b0104","tid":1190594,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1136822496139726848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1136822496139726848&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8upNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=2db72fe8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1136822496139726848&h=72bb6b51\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1136822496139726848</a><br />\n<br />\n香港還有教英國史時，考試會問「處決英皇查理斯一世合理還是不合理？」，前題已承認事實上英皇是可以被處決，無需把君主稱為一夫。過去香港常講的人治和法治，像人治就是英國通俗語言。香港人的特性，源頭是東方和西方；沒有了英史科，沒有了相關英國知識，香港人是衰失了一半。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2yhhJO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2yhhJO.png&h=bf8a0e39&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}